    "title": "Jupiter Hospital International Enterprises is Hiring: Consultant Physician (Senior)",
    "description": "Jupiter Hospital International Enterprises, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Consultant Physician for our Raipur operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Jupiter Hospital International Enterprises:\nJupiter Hospital International Enterprises is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Provide high-quality patient care and maintain patient records\n• Educate patients and families on health management and disease prevention\n• Administer medications and treatments as prescribed\n• Adhere to NABH/JCI accreditation standards\n• Diagnose and treat medical conditions following established protocols\n• Collaborate with pharmaceutical representatives and medical suppliers\n• Participate in quality improvement initiatives and clinical audits\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBBS / MD / MS from recognized medical college\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in EMR/EHR\n• Proficiency in Clinical Documentation\n• Proficiency in NABH Standards\n• Proficiency in HIPAA Compliance\n• Proficiency in Medical Ethics\n• Proficiency in Wound Care\n• Proficiency in Clinical Research\n• Proficiency in Pharmacovigilance\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Learning & development budget\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Flexible working hours\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Raipur, Chhattisgarh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Jupiter Hospital International Enterprises!",
